      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Purpose"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "This is a primary command. Use this command to change the current"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "setting for delete confirmation."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Format"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "CONFIRM [ ON | OFF ]"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Remarks"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "When delete confirmation is ON, SPF/PC will ask you to confirm delete"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "requests made in select lists via the delete line command."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "You can also set delete confirmation on the File List Utility entry"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "panel. See the DELETE command for more information."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Example"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "CONFIRM OFF"
      },
